Package siminov.hybrid.parsers


Class Summary
HybridDescriptorParser Exposes methods to parse Hybrid Descriptor information as per define in HybridDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
HybridLibraryDescriptorParser Exposes methods to parse Library Descriptor information as per define in LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
HybridSiminovDataBuilder Exposes API to build Siminov Hybrid JSON format data to transfer between WEB-TO-NATIVE or NATIVE-TO-WEB.
HybridSiminovDataParser Exposes API to parse Siminov Hybrid JSON format data to transfer between WEB-TO-NATIVE or NATIVE-TO-WEB.
